
prompt_orig_15 = "Find motifs in the following story. For each motif, return 'yes' if the motif is present in the story, return 'no' if the motif is absent. If the motif is modified, add a very short comment next to yes or no. Do not write the motif. Choose among the following motifs: 1. Cruel stepmother, 2. Stepdaughter heroine, 3. Helpful birds, 4. Clothes produced by magic, 5. Fairy as helper, 6. Magic object received from mother, 7. Magic object found on mother‘s grave, 8. Dead mother returns to aid persecuted children, 9. Prince sees heroine at ball and is enamored, 10. Prince sees maiden at church and is enamored, 11. Tabu: staying too long at ball. Must leave before certain hour, 12. Heroine’s three-fold flight from ball, 13. Glass shoes/slippers, 14. Shoe/slipper test. Identification by fitting of shoe/slipper, 15. False bride‘s mutilated feet. In order to wear the shoes/slippers with which the husband is testing the identity of his bride, the false bride cuts her feet. She is detected. Example: 1. yes 2. no etc."

